Scrollgroup class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "GroupClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Scrollgroup class is used to create scrollable virtual groups.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}FreeHoriz@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}FreeVert@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}UseWinBorder@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}VirtgroupContents@{fg text}
  S I
  If supplied, it must be a Virtgroup class object name,
  otherwise the contents of the Scrollgroup is read as an
  ordinary group.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

